{"tid":831992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[曾上游]5層樓私影妹：唔會上客人屋企","createTime":"2018-09-22T12:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T21:53:56.000Z","uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5162a3eac53a84d7c7f84de5fb666d93267ab961","tid":831992,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又係回帶時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名15歲私影少女，前年在客人住所被虐殺，案件轟動全城，而37歲被告劉璋輝，本月中被判囚終身。<br />\n<br />\n曾上游說一定不會上攝影師的住所，也不會去遊艇拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n「經常接觸不同的(陌生)人，危險程度一定比做普通工作的人高，這方面真的要靠自己小心。」現全職做私影妹的曾上游（25歲），就說工作時會格外小心。 <br />\n<br />\n她說一定不會上攝影師的住所，也不會去遊艇拍攝，「因為去住所，沒有閉路電視，攝影師關了門，你便處於被動的位置，會任人魚肉，反抗或脫身的機會較低。上遊艇更危險，因為去到公海，只得兩個人，手機又沒訊號，對方做什麼事，也反抗不了。」 <br />\n<br />\n她表示，多數客人都會要求去酒店或賓館拍攝，當中會有些心懷不軌，「我遇過最多的，是借擺姿勢為由，去毛手毛腳。有一些又會趁你不在意時，觸碰你的臀部和胸部，這樣我會覺得不好受。」 <br />\n<br />\n甚至，會有人要求性交易，「通常有人會問拍照收多少錢，之後便會問，拍得性感收多少錢，之後又會問有沒有其他服務。有一些會拍照時，會問可否加錢做愛。」她說，遇到這情況都會婉轉地拒絕。 <br />\n<br />\n怎樣保護自己呢？「我跟攝影師傾談時，會估計他是怎樣的人，如果他有一些比較奇怪的要求，自己覺得不舒服，都要拒絕。」 <br />\n<br />\n撰文：程志康 <br />\n<br />\n攝影：金文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180324/578232?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180324%2F578232%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=OKT7wwAq0alXNoREpGbchNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4eeeb22f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180324%2F578232%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6fa49a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180324/578232?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"b950d31fde76d49b3dc899e2319497690d837b7a","tid":831992,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"唔會俾人上!"},{"pid":"d32c2595f382cb17d8c558c11962721a7ae6b3f7","tid":831992,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"同場加映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/c0.10.540.282/p540x282/42076325_716210742060763_8071589321351626752_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;oh=dda8b4b870584fe7882d530f8d1a5716&amp;oe=5C24FABD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fc0.10.540.282%2Fp540x282%2F42076325_716210742060763_8071589321351626752_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26oh%3Ddda8b4b870584fe7882d530f8d1a5716%26oe%3D5C24FABD&h=cf48bc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【五層樓港女評廢青】港男無料扮四條 港女曾上游：傾好條件至一齊（足本版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180921/625169?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180921%2F625169%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=OKT7wwAq0alXNoREpGbchNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c9ceee82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180921%2F625169%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextma